author: sichen
msg: ShipmentReceipt has no shipmentItemSeqId field and shipmentItemSeqId is a required field for ShipmentItemBilling, so don't create a ShipmentItemBilling record for invoice items created as the result of a purchase shipment. What really needs to happen is for ShipmentReceipt to have a shipmentItemSeqId field, but this is a lower-impact fix for now.
